{"tid":469848,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"當時的小小遊記","createTime":"2017-11-15T17:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T17:58:00.000Z","uid":22727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0f2898d739846bbfd2f4cc2b4ffe24bce35ccd","tid":469848,"uid":22727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:33:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n小弟係前排(幾年前)就去左歐洲行下<br />\n<br />\n咁返到黎先突然想寫返個小小遊記<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我成績本身就唔好 再成日諗住&quot;讀萬卷書不如行萬里路&quot;<br />\n<br />\n所以當時DSE考完oral就同朋友走左去行萬里路<br />\n<br />\n而係過程當中明白 如果你無知識就去行萬里路呢<br />\n<br />\n盡其量你都只係一個郵差 而我 好成功咁成為一位郵差<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/012722_dc976b79d87803cdf93ffa9c1763d13e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F012722_dc976b79d87803cdf93ffa9c1763d13e.jpg&h=f3e1b4a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n選擇荷蘭作為第一站既原因只係同行既一位朋友有親戚住係度<br />\n<br />\n而係荷蘭既行程可以話係佢既親戚一手包辦曬<br />\n<br />\n所以啱啱畢業既我地係同Amsterdam最有名既紅燈區同大資都係無緣既<br />\n<br />\n以為有紅燈區相既巴打可能要失望啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當時一落機就好成功咁俾入境處捉左入間房度問野啦<br />\n<br />\n以當時我既英文水平同未成為連登仔前既推理能力去分析<br />\n<br />\n得出既結果係無結果既<br />\n<br />\n再係大家有限度既身體語言加英文單詞上終於借到電話打俾朋友個親戚<br />\n<br />\n糾纏左一個半鐘之後終於成功離開  8:00正式出發去第一個景點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/012734_ffc79947044b3cbe590d0d08034cbedb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F012734_ffc79947044b3cbe590d0d08034cbedb.jpg&h=b21bcb4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n風車村﹣Zaanse Schans<br />\n<br />\n相信大部份巴打對呢個地點都唔陌生架啦<br />\n<br />\n每個去荷蘭既朋友都一定會黎呢個地方<br />\n<br />\n而入面除左風車之外 就係木鞋同乳酪工廠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/012743_93efeef295faedd4aabc0893dd983881.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F012743_93efeef295faedd4aabc0893dd983881.jpg&h=c2d0268b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/012753_b677d1735e3a1513a24041ba4df87184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F012753_b677d1735e3a1513a24041ba4df87184.jpg&h=1b766e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/012757_86bfb8eaea73112279b82e16339089e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F012757_86bfb8eaea73112279b82e16339089e6.jpg&h=41ee6567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/012800_d271ecf156ac3d3b99b54df5cfdbb748.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F012800_d271ecf156ac3d3b99b54df5cfdbb748.jpg&h=3ddade9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而當時既我以為木鞋只係整黎間中玩下著下咁<br />\n<br />\n原來以前既農民又真係會著黎落田種野<br />\n<br />\n咁搵返資料就話木鞋係泥地行就輕巧少少 又易整易洗同防潮<br />\n<br />\n所以當地人就好鍾意著呢啲木鞋啦  咁資料就係事後上網睇返既<br />\n<br />\n以上既相都係我當時影既<br />\n<br />\n品質肯定就唔達標架啦 希望各位巴打見諒<br />\n<br />\n聽晚應該會再出既  之後應該會補返多少少資料性既野<br />\n<br />\n而相就盡量睇下搵唔搵得返多少少"},{"pid":"55a6ba1a1b7033dfa6313603508b723ae41def4b","tid":469848,"uid":5163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:58:00.000Z","msg":"沙發"}]}